00:34:18.870 --> 00:34:23.179
And so that strategy
has to include

00:34:23.179 --> 00:34:26.030
the specific kinds of
targeted efforts like perhaps

00:34:26.030 --> 00:34:27.030
you've been involved in.

00:34:27.030 --> 00:34:29.940
And those are really
important to continue doing.

00:34:29.940 --> 00:34:32.100
And I commend you for doing it.

00:34:32.100 --> 00:34:34.444
On the other hand, it also
takes other kinds of social--

00:34:34.444 --> 00:34:36.360
